--- Debian 11 ---

Build dependencies:

  sudo apt install autoconf libgtk-3-0 \
    librsvg2-dev libpng-dev libjansson-dev \
    libjansson4 mailutils libtiff-dev libtiff5 \
    libgif-dev libxpm-dev libgnutls28-dev libxml2-dev

Runtime dependencies (DOOM):

  sudo apt install \
    glslang-tools \
    shellcheck \
    npm \
    markdown

--- Arch Linux ---

Build dependencies:

  doas pacman -S libjpeg-turbo librsvg \
    jansson mailutils libtiff giflib \
    libxpm gnutls libxml2 libgccjit

